        "created_at": "2022-04-29T20:59:36.229Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Is it possible to check if the IP-address matches the client-ip?</p>\n<p>E.g. Cerficicate for the client <code>10.1.2.3</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-auto\">openssl ... -addext \"subjectAltName=IP:10.1.2.3\"\n</code></pre>\n<p>Something like:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-auto\">tls_verify_peers = Check.Valid=S.subjectAltName=IP:&lt;remote-ip&gt;\n</code></pre>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 3,
        "updated_at": "2022-04-29T20:59:36.229Z",
        "reply_count": 0,
